                    <span>I love Eckhart Tolle and the content of these Cds is beautiful.
<br />BUT this 2-CD set is already part of another 6-CD set entitled "Realizing the Power of Now: An In-Depth Retreat With Eckhart Tolle".
<br />The point is that it is not clearly stated (unless you click on the cover picture to magnify it) and .....they have even used for this product a different title, colour and graphics! 
<br />As I bought both sets at the same time, when I found it out I felt cheated.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Entering the Now (The Power of Now Teaching Series) [ABRIDGE</div>
